snippet.title: Dancin Divas Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wish-list on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1941370/Dancin_Divas/
A robbery has taken place! Four Diva's from around the world are showcasing their treasures at the local lounge but things have gone south. It's time to fight back!
